data.title: Episode 2560 (29 July 2003)
data.meta_description: Garry attends to Bobby and Laura. Joanne confesses that she has feelings for Phil. Meanwhile, Little Mo gets Charlie to lend Billy the money he needs. 'Little' Mo Mitchell - Kacey Ainsworth Billy Mitchell - Perry Fenwick Dot Branning - June Brown Jim Branning - John Bardon Charlie Slater - Derek...
data.text:
Little Mo is frantic because Billy didn't come home the night before.

Laura is relieved to hear that her baby is going to be fine but is worried about what to tell Garry now she realises that the baby isn't his.

Dan is anxious that Adi's new girlfriend can't attend the family wedding.

Alfie is bemused to find that Billy has spent the night in the Vic's toilets.

Jim receives a mystery letter.

Little Mo tries to make Billy feel better about himself but let's slip that she has been successful herself.
